<br>
<br>Large, eat in kitchen with ample cabinet and counter space. New gas stove, hood and dishwasher as well as refrigerator. 
<br>
<br>Two very good-sized bedrooms are overlooking the back yard.  One of the bedrooms with direct backyard access through sliding doors. 3rd bedroom on this main floor is also good in size. Full size, recently remodeled bathroom on this main floor with shower over tub.   
